        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "Our labour tills the soil, our dung fertilises it, and yet there is not one of us that owns more than his bare skin",
          "target": "我们的劳动耕耘土壤，我们的粪肥滋养它，然而我们中没有一个人拥有超过他光秃秃的皮肤"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "The pigs did not actually work, but directed and supervised the others. With their superior knowledge it was natural that they should assume the leadership",
          "target": "猪们实际上并不工作，而是指挥和监督其他动物。凭借他们优越的知识，他们自然应该承担领导角色"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "research shows that the single biggest cause of work burnout is not work overload, but working too long without experiencing your own personal development",
          "target": "研究表明，导致工作倦怠的最大原因不是工作过量，而是长时间工作却没有体验到个人发展"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "Challenge existing processes Inspire a shared vision",
          "target": "挑战现有流程 激发共同愿景"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "higher level of independence, self-reliance, self-trust, and the capacity to exercise initiative",
          "target": "更高水平的独立性、自力更生、自信以及行使主动权的能力"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "I lived at number twenty-three Blenheim Road for five years, blissfully happy and utterly wretched",
          "target": "我在布伦海姆路23号住了五年，既无比幸福又极度痛苦"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "Life is not a paragraph, and death is no parenthesis",
          "target": "生命不是段落，死亡也不是括号"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "The street is clear—no sign of Tom or Anna—and the part of me that can’t resist a bit of drama is actually quite disappointed",
          "target": "街道上空无一人——没有汤姆或安娜的踪影——而我内心那部分无法抗拒一点戏剧性的部分实际上相当失望"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "but failure cloaked me like a mantle, it overwhelmed me, dragged me under, and I gave up hope",
          "target": "但失败像斗篷一样笼罩着我，它压倒了我，把我拖入深渊，我放弃了希望"
        },
